{"tid":329334,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"呀朗在床上打飛機","createTime":"2017-07-20T09:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T17:14:32.000Z","uid":18605,"like":30,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7063ee35dc942529f9d3952283738a70dcf396e5","tid":329334,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T09:42:48.000Z","msg":"夜闌人靜，只有呀朗一個的房間，仿佛塵世間一切繁囂，都與我無關。他閉上眼睛，享受那都市繁囂中的片刻寧靜。<br />\n<br />\n世界越繁榮，對呀朗而言就繁瑣。不必要的規矩，被迫活着的節奏，無厘頭的加班。<br />\n<br />\n這個晚上，對呀朗而言，十分奢侈。<br />\n<br />\n軟熟的床墊已躺出一個凹印，聞到枕頭裡殘留的洗頭水味，突然回想起上星期與女友在這凹痕上翻雲覆雨。<br />\n<br />\n將回憶在腦海重播幾次，呀朗的小弟早已肅然起敬，他屈指一算，心想「好像好久沒打了...」"},{"pid":"9b4c229e388e4329d15da022f8d2904ff1f4440b","tid":329334,"uid":18605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T09:48:44.000Z","msg":"他拿起手機，解鎖，點開Thisxx，為接下來要做的事情作準備。<br />\n<br />\n一頁......兩頁......三頁......<br />\n<br />\n他手指在屏幕上滑過了無數影片，突然被一個片名吸引。<br />\n<br />\n呀朗二話不說，點進影片。<br />\n<br />\n「屌，中伏。」一個四十路熟女從屏幕出現。"},{"pid":"5ca06cd1490a066ad96f13481be2b467ab122978","tid":329334,"uid":18605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T09:53:42.000Z","msg":"AV，人類史上最偉大的發明，它陪伴過多少寂寞的人。<br />\n<br />\nAV，人類史上最偉大的發明，它培植過多少年少氣盛的少年。<br />\n<br />\n一套合格的av，理應使人熱血沸騰，血壓直飆。<br />\n<br />\n不過，這套av卻使人下半旗致哀。"},{"pid":"63757916faffca54634ead18bc9c17bb38220de7","tid":329334,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T09:56:33.000Z","msg":"點過三百二十四條片段，換言之呀朗一夜之間中過三百多個伏。<br />\n<br />\n呀朗心諗，這個世界活得太累了。<br />\n<br />\n就連打個飛機都需花盡腦力。"},{"pid":"bed2ee72584ab7eb1dbaa7ae2fe4a3419d27aad0","tid":329334,"uid":17397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T09:57:54.000Z","msg":"打飛機都有故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceceb3b1ace68d7f64ddd65e42afb6cbcc9d9035","tid":329334,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:01:19.000Z","msg":"呀朗終於找到一套合意的av，原本寧靜的世界，被淫賤的喊聲取締。<br />\n<br />\n看着av女優的玲瓏浮凸，又想起女友的乾衰扁平，呀朗心諗：唉"},{"pid":"9bf7bcb55b595fc85f90f73346578f151a462534","tid":329334,"uid":18605,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:07:48.000Z","msg":"呀朗無意間將注意力放到女優的身材上。<br />\n<br />\n標緻的五官，略尖的下巴，豐滿的乳房......還有一排六格整齊的腹肌。<br />\n<br />\n看到這裡，呀朗手部的動作停止了。<br />\n<br />\n將手機挪開一點，向下望自己的腹部。<br />\n<br />\n一...... 二 ...... 三 ......<br />\n<br />\n有三條線。三條清晰，而又深刻的線。"},{"pid":"1003f68e9e7d89249394ee9e9182a0401c3efb0b","tid":329334,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:08:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打飛機都有故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫雞都有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb19ea11ae9b64c146f511a7a4c67b0d20458c03","tid":329334,"uid":62850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:18:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打飛機都有故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫雞都有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁叫雞可歌可泣得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ec29067ab11488676c8fc1a573b0b73cac905f","tid":329334,"uid":18605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:18:20.000Z","msg":"呀朗好想哭，從小以來，呀朗都比不上誰。<br />\n<br />\n誰是誰？誰知道。<br />\n<br />\n可能是中學的同學，可能是鄰壁的小明，可能是𨋢口碰到的誰。<br />\n<br />\n如今，連一個AV女優都比不上。<br />\n<br />\n呀朗心傷，但無從抒發。<br />\n<br />\n他轉換畫面，轉到lihkg，將今晚的事，寫下來。呀朗情願做瘋子，也不要做失敗者。<br />\n<br />\n睡吧。呀朗對自己說<br />\n<br />\n或許明天會更好。"},{"pid":"184a93ed525628a48076ea1d5dddd47b067c3c1c","tid":329334,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:19:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>打飛機都有故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫雞都有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁叫雞可歌可泣得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打飛機仲慘喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得右手陪伴<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7387056d74a0574ca440c62eea8ad6a773ac75f","tid":329334,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:35:29.000Z","msg":"係咪到我接龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d739cbce8b11178c1da6425a966acadbd4f9a528","tid":329334,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:56:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪到我接龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n接到就來<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2336c3f2f6650091c3b7afdf9003550cde69b7de","tid":329334,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T11:12:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪到我接龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n接到就來<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好，開始打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e04dc6357aa2a438bc08bf01593e8d74b32978","tid":329334,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T11:19:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係咪到我接龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n接到就來<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好，開始打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你都接到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8548cfd25bc105e4fc21415ddc804b2a56fd1ef","tid":329334,"uid":127768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T11:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d940bdc63d18fa240bfe91f8c746b3540c7d46","tid":329334,"uid":17354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T11:36:39.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"5a67987543e5b18c1de460c948e303b259d0b22b","tid":329334,"uid":72590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T12:06:11.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"4eb41fc36c77f9ab26dee5da0a129c94bcab5c36","tid":329334,"uid":38861,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T12:14:12.000Z","msg":"在睡夢中，我憶起了大學生活時的點點滴滴; <br />\n<br />\n我坐在香港大學的邵逸夫禮堂裡，四旁均全滿了同科的同學，有的在玩著手機，有的在低頭淺睡。<br />\n<br />\n大家各自成群，有說有笑。<br />\n<br />\n正因如此，真正聆聽台上教授課堂內容的學生，十根手指可以數得清清楚楚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就在此時，女教授突然間叫上我的全名，問上一條極具尖銳性的問題。<br />\n「沙時朗，你可否向大家講解一下打飛機的好處嗎?」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這條問題觸動了到在座所有熱血青年的神經，大家全都寂靜起來，把目光投向到我的方位。<br />\n<br />\n「好處...是會得到快感....」<br />\n我整塊臉紅了起來，用著極尷尬的聲線回答。<br />\n<br />\n聽到我這個答案後，整個會堂突然間充滿了恥笑的聲音，不少人更掩著嘴指著我竊笑起來。<br />\n<br />\n嘖，我有說錯嗎?<br />\n<br />\n打飛機的好處...不就是為了求開心嗎?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「肅靜!」<br />\n台上的那位女教授露大聲的作出命令; 雖然她的聲線非常的威嚴，但我亦看得出她不經意的恥笑了我一下。<br />\n<br />\n「多謝沙同學的答案。<br />\n<br />\n根據2016年3月美國的一份學術研究，男性打飛機的次數是與前列腺癌患病的機率是成反比關係的。<br />\n即是，打飛機的好處就是能夠減低前列腺癌的機率。」<br />\n<br />\n嘩! 全場突然傳出一片嘩然的聲音，不少人露出了難以置信的樣子，表示無法相信台上的女教授會說出這一番的說話。<br />\n<br />\n「真的嗎?」<br />\n<br />\n「不會吧!」<br />\n眾男生露出喜悅的神情，雀躍的談論了起來。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然而，在眾人起哄的時候，我身後突然傳出一把嬌嗲的女聲。<br />\n「呀朗!」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我向後一望，只見我女友赤裸裸的與我對望著。她左手輕撫著我的臉頰，在我耳旁溫柔的說<br />\n「竟然教授也這樣說，不如讓我來幫你防癌吧!」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啪!<br />\n我閉上了雙眼，隱弱的聽到皮帶鬆脫的聲音................<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希又希希又希，團結一心有新轉機...<br />\n<br />\n就在快要進行防癌工程的時候，手機的聆聲突然間響了起來，把我從夢中喚回到現實殘酷的世界。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我看著雪白的天花板，不自覺的落淚了;<br />\n<br />\n想不到在現實上甚麼也做不成的我，在夢中也是一樣的沒用，連打飛機這般小事也完成不到。<br />\n<br />\n我懷著悕憈的心情，拿起了床頭的手機一看，只見有一個新的私人訊息。<br />\n<br />\n「早上三時正<br />\n寄件人:不明<br />\n收件人:沙時朗<br />\n<br />\n你今天打了飛機沒有?」"},{"pid":"a2ad19a091f1c284d4274e8fb6d4dc180e690ad1","tid":329334,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T12:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d09f3757ac5bea29e157214794c138566a6ca6","tid":329334,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T12:20:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n到你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好9寫hea我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d002e49050d06e5545573834f9da47274182db5","tid":329334,"uid":18605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T12:23:24.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n<br />\n呀朗覆了這麼一句<br />\n<br />\n然後繼續上班上學"},{"pid":"a58fe072cf2ff7dae08195a3de212d1dea872a6e","tid":329334,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T12:23:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇<br />\n<br />\n呀朗覆了這麼一句<br />\n<br />\n然後繼續上班上學</blockquote><br />\n&lt;完&gt;"},{"pid":"10682b724b1bec698ecc986065bf43c0998b259d","tid":329334,"uid":91322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T12:24:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n到你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好9寫hea我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會太強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbcd486825bc251b8b5484b8ed561f09473f14ef","tid":329334,"uid":99364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T12:25:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"294be7e3ce78711f5d2332a096e9bfb295726b79","tid":329334,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T12:28:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇<br />\n<br />\n呀朗覆了這麼一句<br />\n<br />\n然後繼續上班上學</blockquote><br />\n&lt;完&gt;</blockquote><br />\n上咗熱門呀，完咩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n寫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b75df0db4e87c9e746388f173fcc37aff1d6e16","tid":329334,"uid":29726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T12:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f7a71c9265f335d4b12156077925973f157ecb","tid":329334,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T12:58:33.000Z","msg":"打緊"},{"pid":"3dba42bbc7053f79a0f6e3d627c939fa41f26fde","tid":329334,"uid":82436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T12:59:40.000Z","msg":"打飛機都有故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78e12d29e9c36251c7187456c21fa784bb927174","tid":329334,"uid":95519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T13:04:03.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1038b921e877ad94b6