ike":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:07:24.000Z","msg":"是誰？收到訊息的呀朗感到疑惑，明明是毒撚──有女的毒撚，誰會主動找他？以為只是看到幻覺。<br />\n<br />\n不對！有女，怎會是毒撚。呀朗反對<br />\n<br />\n呀朗又反問自己：哪......你像毒撚嗎？<br />\n<br />\n呀朗在鏡子前打量自己，油得發亮的頭髮，千古不變的薯頭，懷胎七月的大肚......<br />\n<br />\n「也蠻像......不對！單憑外表怎能斷定我是毒撚？」呀朗反駁自己。<br />\n<br />\n「那麼......你有朋友嗎？」呀朗問自己。<br />\n<br />\n「有......女朋友......」呀朗心知，這個答案，卑微得很。<br />\n<br />\n「有社交嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n「......」呀朗無言以對。<br />\n<br />\n「沒朋友，沒社交，就是毒撚。」呀朗為呀朗判上最終死刑，呀朗無法上訴......也無從上訢。<br />\n<br />\n「嗯，我是毒撚。」<br />\n<br />\n呀朗確認了自己是毒撚，不過是有女友的特殊存在。<br />\n<br />\n「希也希也希......」電話鈴聲將呀朗帶回現實。<br />\n<br />\n「今日打左飛機未？」<br />\n<br />\n同樣的聯絡人，同一句句子，發到同一手機。<br />\n<br />\n呀朗確認自己沒有幻覺。於是回覆：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n05:00a.m                           「誰？」<br />\n<br />\n「重要嗎？」05:01a.m<br />\n<br />\n05:02a.m              「屌你老母梗係重要啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後，對方沒有再回覆。<br />\n<br />\n果然，只是一個惡作劇，一個不知哪來的惡作劇，呀朗十分眼瞓，想繼續倒在床上睡覺。<br />\n<br />\n「啪！」在枱上的水杯突然倒下了，一嚇之下，他下意識向後踏步，屁股又撞倒了一物。<br />\n<br />\n此時，枱上那準備用來打飛機的紙巾被一陣怪風吹動起來，然後又靜止了，接着他感到背脊一涼，一股未知氣流掃過了他全身。<br />\n<br />\n「快要天亮......沒那麼邪門吧......」<br />\n<br />\n那股氣流從身體左邊掃過右邊，然後又慢慢地回來從右掃回左......<br />\n<br />\n呀朗手心冒汗，心跳急升。<br />\n<br />\n後面......有東西......<br />\n<br />\n他嚥口水，慢慢地回頭......看到鏡子邊緣，呀朗緊閉雙眼，慢慢把整個人轉到背後，又一陣陰風吹過身體，連小弟都不放過。<br />\n<br />\n慢慢張開眼睛......發現......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來自己未著褲......<br />\n<br />\n怪風是掉在地的風扇吹起。<br />\n<br />\n「屌！」呀朗發自內心，由衷地爆了句粗。<br />\n<br />\n「希也希也希......」突然鈴聲響起。<br />\n<br />\n「哇屌！」呀朗又一次發自內心地爆了粗，差點沒嚇得跳起來。<br />\n<br />\n驚魂未定的呀朗看到手機「我是你的朋友。」<br />\n<br />\n我是你的朋友。<br />\n<br />\n朋友......<br />\n<br />\n朋友......<br />\n<br />\n朋友......二字重重錘下呀朗的心......<br />\n<br />\n呀朗被這個陌生人深深感動了......<br />\n<br />\n「人生......如夢，朋友...... 如霧......」有誰會直接了當告訴你是自己的朋友？<br />\n<br />\n就是真正把你當朋友的人！<br />\n<br />\n呀朗熱淚盈眶，心內的感動此刻無法以筆墨來形容，那就像是沙漠中找到了綠洲，在茫茫大海中找到了浮木，呀朗決定要好好認真對待這位朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後他決定繼續瞓覺。<br />\n<br />\n睡夢中，他隱若聽到手機發出「希也希也希......」的聲音，但他已沉進那睡夢之中，再也聽不到了......"},{"pid":"4b5df92a23814ac4fdd0802c90c560a4045cdd15","tid":329334,"uid":35833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:26:52.000Z","msg":"遲啲會唔會話咩打打下條J會突然間變身拯救世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69ccc61aededaf1d15167b1a5033e0a2bf976a6","tid":329334,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:35:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遲啲會唔會話咩打打下條J會突然間變身拯救世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇薯仔點寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我盡量唔比佢暴走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c4672f3b309d0077760f020779d54bfa4ab115","tid":329334,"uid":5647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:38:43.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de3a1ab26cb2dbfa2db0467a8255fab886249f6","tid":329334,"uid":18605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:44:11.000Z","msg":"解釋下個po嘅由來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n是咁的，小弟某日心血來潮起來騎劫左薯仔聞茱莉巴打個蛋牛治po，<del>一騎之下，薯仔反而比我騎上癮</del><br />\n然後又喺薯仔聞茱莉嘅po度鳩up故事大綱，然後薯仔就話「掂喎，不如你開個新po同你玩鳩故接龍呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」然後呢個po就誕生了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">我係唔會講呢個po原本係我無聊得濟所以鳩打左篇文而引起架</span></span>"},{"pid":"fe4680dae713cd0158fd0b71b4ed9d147cbc044d","tid":329334,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:49:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2288ea7d8fc97d2a5b76c9567276a9198686773d","tid":329334,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:51:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>救命啊兩個黐線佬啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好正常"},{"pid":"b414015fd1ca21df5cd7c255d2b0cabcf43b40df","tid":329334,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:51:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>打緊</blockquote><br />\nbtw,你係咪現實間識我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能係 可能唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n相認啦!!</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b68a1cd516b08e4c286c552b46f388ecd6b67f8","tid":329334,"uid":118642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T19:28:39.000Z","msg":"咁似李小明既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d805e0346d1f55ab1545c26db1c4b69d9f3d235e","tid":329334,"uid":35301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T01:22:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57fc307c72963280053a3ab2aa7d5ea9be30c150","tid":32